[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1057","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1057.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1341","title":"Linux 内核 SLIP/PPP IP 数据包伪造漏洞","description":"Linux 2.3.18 之前版本及 2.2.13pre15 之前版本的内核中，当启用 SLIP 和 PPP 选项时存在 IP 数据包伪造漏洞。本地低权限用户可通过向 tty 设备发送 TIOCSETD ioctl 选项，将终端线路设置为 SLIP 模式，从而绕过内核的源地址校验机制伪造任意 IP 数据包。攻击者利用此漏洞可冒充其他主机发送伪造的网络流量，实施 IP 欺骗攻击，导致中间人攻击或拒绝服务等后果。该漏洞影响启用了 SLIP/PPP 模块的 Linux 系统，攻击者需具备本地 shell 访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1341"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-22","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.3.18 及以上版本，或 2.2.13 正式版及以上版本，即可修复此漏洞。如无法升级内核，可卸载或禁用 SLIP 和 PPP 内核模块（modprobe -r slip ppp），并限制普通用户对 tty 设备 TIOCSETD ioctl 的访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94061108411308&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7858","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1341"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1057.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1057.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0700","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0700.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0766","title":"Microsoft Java Virtual Machine 沙箱逃逸远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Java 虚拟机（JVM）存在安全沙箱逃逸漏洞，恶意 Java Applet 小程序可利用该漏洞绕过 JVM 的安全沙箱限制，在目标系统上执行任意命令。攻击者只需诱导用户访问包含恶意 Applet 的网页即可触发攻击，无需任何身份认证。该漏洞影响 Microsoft 实现的 Java 虚拟机，危害等级严重，CVSS 评分 9.3。微软已发布安全更新修复此漏洞，建议用户禁用 Java Applet 支持或安装相应补丁。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0766"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-10-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.830","remediation":"立即卸载 Microsoft Java Virtual Machine（通过\"添加/删除程序\"或运行 `msiexec /x {08B20019-0A8E-11D3-BF9F-00C04F8EFB7C}`），改用 Oracle Java 或 OpenJDK 最新版本。在 IIS 中禁用 Java 支持，移除 class 文件 MIME 映射。在防火墙和代理层面拦截 .class 文件下载。对于必须使用 Microsoft JVM 的遗留系统，安装 MS00-075 安全更新 (Q318203)。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ240346","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/600","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-031"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0700.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0704","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0704.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0905","title":"Axent Raptor Firewall 6.0 IP Options Zero Length 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Axent Raptor Firewall 6.0 在处理 IP 选项时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的零长度 IP 选项数据包，导致防火墙处理逻辑异常而崩溃或停止响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Axent Raptor Firewall 6.0 版本，攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0905"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.040","remediation":"该漏洞影响 Axent Raptor Firewall 6.0，厂商已于 2000 年被 Symantec 收购，产品已停止支持。建议升级至 Axent Raptor 6.5 或更高版本以修复此问题；如无法升级，可在上游路由器或防火墙上配置 ACL 丢弃包含畸形或零长度 IP 选项的数据包作为临时缓解。长远建议迁移至现代受支持的防火墙产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1121","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/736","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19564"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0704.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0691","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0691.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0895","title":"Check Point FireWall-1 LDAP属性访问控制不当漏洞","description":"Check Point Firewall-1 存在访问控制不当漏洞，未正确限制对 LDAP 属性的访问权限。远程攻击者可通过精心构造的 LDAP 请求绕过安全策略，获取或修改敏感目录信息。该漏洞影响 Check Point Firewall-1 特定版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，建议用户及时升级至厂商修复版本以消除风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0895"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.810","remediation":"升级 Check Point FireWall-1 至 4.1 Service Pack 2 或更高版本，该版本已修复 LDAP 属性访问控制缺陷。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙规则中限制对 LDAP 服务器 389/TCP 端口的访问，仅允许受信任的管理工作站连接，同时关闭 User Manager 中不必要的匿名 LDAP 查询功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1117","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/725","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=19991020150002.21047.qmail%40tarjan.mediaways.net"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0691.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0897","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0897.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1047","title":"BSDI Gauntlet 安全绕过漏洞","description":"BSDI 为 Gauntlet 5.0 防火墙提供的安全补丁若未按正确顺序安装，将导致防火墙访问控制规则失效，远程攻击者可绕过防火墙的访问限制直接访问受保护的内部网络资源。同时，该漏洞还会导致防火墙无法记录绕过攻击的日志，使得攻击行为难以被追溯和检测。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1047"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:35.700","remediation":"确保按 BSDI 官方文档指定的正确顺序安装 Gauntlet 5.0 补丁，先安装内核补丁再安装防火墙组件补丁。若无法确认顺序，建议卸载后按依赖关系重新安装所有补丁：先安装 BSDI OS 基础补丁，再安装 Gauntlet 补丁包。由于该产品已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的防火墙方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94026690521279&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94036662326185&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/3397.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1047.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1047","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1047.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1047.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1047.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hf63-g73x-xwcf/GHSA-hf63-g73x-xwcf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1047.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000827.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0897.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1058","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1058.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1342","title":"这是实际的字段内容","description":"ICQ ActiveList Server 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向服务器 UDP 端口发送特制的畸形数据包，导致服务进程崩溃。该漏洞源于对畸形数据包的处理不当，无需身份认证即可触发，影响运行 ICQ ActiveList Server 的系统。攻击者只需具备网络访问能力即可实施攻击，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1342"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:14.200","remediation":"ICQ ActiveList Server 已于 2000 年代初停止维护，官方未发布任何安全补丁。建议立即停止使用该产品，迁移至受支持的即时通讯服务端方案。如因遗留系统无法立即下线，可在防火墙层面限制对服务器 UDP 端口（默认 4000）的访问，仅允许可信 IP 来源，以降低被攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94042342010662&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/af5cedcf472f3690d94c4249ff35246f15692534/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1342.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1342","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1342.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1342.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wvfc-q7gw-9hp6/GHSA-wvfc-q7gw-9hp6.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1342.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/cd16675cc1e3e922479c321a4eb330fe6d02d2d4/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--6e8f212f-9047-4f84-b5e0-5172ba3cd103.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1058.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1400","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1400.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0943","title":"OpenLink Software OpenLink 3.2 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"OpenLink Software OpenLink 3.2 的 Web 配置器存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的超长 GET 请求触发缓冲区溢出，导致远程代码执行或权限提升。该漏洞影响 OpenLink 3.2 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，成功利用可完全控制受影响系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0943"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:22.660","remediation":"建议升级至 OpenLink 4.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复 Web 配置器中对 GET 请求长度未做边界检查的问题。如无法升级，可在网络层通过防火墙限制对 Web 配置器端口（默认为 TCP 2611）的访问，仅允许受信任管理 IP 连接，同时在应用层实施输入长度校验，限制 GET 请求 URI 长度不超过 1024 字节。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/720","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19558"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1400.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1059","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1059.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1343","title":"Xerox DocuColor 4 LP Fiery Web 服务器拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Xerox DocuColor 4 LP 打印机的 Fiery Web 服务器（基于 Apache/1.0.3）存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过发送包含大量英文句点（约2000个）的畸形 URL 请求，导致 HTTP 服务完全挂起，打印机无法响应 ping 请求且无法执行打印任务，必须通过硬重启才能恢复正常。该漏洞源于服务器对超长 URL 中特殊字符序列的处理缺陷。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1343"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-13","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"Xerox 已停止支持该型号，建议用户：1) 在防火墙上限制对打印机 80 端口的访问，仅允许可信 IP；2) 禁用 Fiery Web 工具中的 HTTP 服务；3) 升级到受支持的打印机型号以获得安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T13:03:49.495911724+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93986405412867&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1059.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0689","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0689.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0893","title":"SCO OpenServer 5.0.5 userOsa 本地符号链接漏洞","description":"SCO OpenServer 5.0.5 系统中的 userOsa 程序存在符号链接（symlink）漏洞，具有本地访问权限的攻击者可通过创建指向任意系统文件的符号链接，诱使该程序以当前权限跟踪链接并写入数据，从而破坏或覆盖目标文件。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer 5.0.5 版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，攻击前提是需要拥有本地系统账户。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0893"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.557","remediation":"建议升级至 SCO OpenServer 5.0.6 或更高版本，该版本已修复 userOsa 符号链接问题。如无法升级，可手动移除 userOsa 的 setuid 权限位（执行 chmod u-s /usr/bin/userOsa），阻止普通用户通过符号链接覆盖系统文件。同时应严格限制本地用户对系统的交互式登录权限，并配置文件系统监控以检测可疑的符号链接创建行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0893","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19542"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0689.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0928","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0928.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1082","title":"t. hauck Jana WebServer 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Jana WebServer 1.0/1.40/1.45/1.46 存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向服务器发送特制的 \"\"（修改的路径遍历）请求，绕过路径限制访问服务器文件系统上的任意文件。此漏洞允许攻击者读取敏感配置文件或系统文件，可能导致进一步的信息泄露或攻击面扩大。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1082"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.017","remediation":"Jana WebServer 产品已停止维护，建议立即停用并迁移至 Apache、Nginx 等活跃维护的 Web 服务器。同时应在 Web 应用入口处配置输入过滤，阻止包含 \"..\" 及变异形式的路径遍历请求。如暂时无法迁移，需在反向代理层面限制文件访问范围并启用 URL 规范化校验。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93941794201059&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/699"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0928.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0928.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0928.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0929","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0929.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1083","title":"Jana Web Server 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Jana Web Server 1.45 及之前版本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向服务器发送包含 `../` 序列的特制 HTTP 请求，突破路径限制访问服务器文件系统上的任意文件（如配置文件、系统文件等），导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Jana Server 1.0/1.45/1.46 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1083"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.140","remediation":"立即升级至 Jana Server 1.46 及以上版本，该版本已修复目录遍历问题。如厂商已停止维护，建议迁移至 Apache httpd 或 Nginx 等现代 Web 服务器。若无法迁移，应在 Web 服务器前端部署反向代理（如 Nginx），并通过 WAF 规则拦截包含 `../` 的 URL 请求路径作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=95730430727064&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/699","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19540","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1083.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1083.json","https://github.com/geeknik/the-nuclei-templates/blob/36a6d14bce3293907a83afb498caec5fd45b1777/CVE-1999-1083.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1083","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1083.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1083.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1083.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w32h-rgfp-2fc4/GHSA-w32h-rgfp-2fc4.json","https://github.com/srkgupta/cent-nuclei-templates/blob/7994d13b8b8c437c9cd4ba33b0e0a63676a91ddd/templates/CVE-1999-1083.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0929.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1064","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1064.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1347","title":"Red Hat Linux Xsession 安全限制绕过漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 6.1 及更早版本中的 Xsession 组件存在安全绕过漏洞。具有受限账户的本地用户可通过从 kdm 登录管理器启动 KDE、GNOME 或其他桌面环境，绕过 .xsession 文件的执行限制，从而获取非授权的桌面环境访问权限。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 6.1 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。攻击者需要拥有本地账户且能够物理或远程登录系统，利用门槛较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1347"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:14.813","remediation":"升级至 Red Hat Linux 6.2 及以上版本，该版本已修复 Xsession 脚本对 kdm 启动桌面环境的权限校验。如无法升级，可修改 /etc/X11/xdm/Xsession 脚本，在启动 kde/gnome 前增加用户权限检查逻辑，或限制 kdm 仅允许授权用户登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93942774609925&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7638326ff3f30ccdb52a67547408dd61f5cdc6cc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1347.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1347","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1347.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1347.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h9h2-mfx3-9xhg/GHSA-h9h2-mfx3-9xhg.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1347.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000818.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ee9754343b23d8c0f998865ae48a5d400d72ba81/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1064.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1063","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1063.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1346","title":"Red Hat Linux rlogin PAM 配置安全绕过漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 6.1 及更早版本中 rlogin 的 PAM 配置文件存在安全绕过漏洞。由于 PAM 规则配置顺序不当，宽松规则位于严格规则之前，导致即使管理员通过 /etc/nologin 文件明确禁用了 rlogin 登录，攻击者仍可利用该配置缺陷绕过限制，通过 rlogin 服务远程访问目标系统。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 6.1 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1346"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-07","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Red Hat Linux 至 6.2 或更高版本，或手动修改 /etc/pam.d/rlogin 配置文件，将检查 /etc/nologin 的限制规则置于宽松规则之前，确保禁用 rlogin 的配置生效。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93942774609925&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1063.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0777","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0777.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0791","title":"Hybrid Networks Cable Broadband Access System 未授权访问漏洞","description":"Hybrid Networks 线缆宽带接入系统 1.0 的管理接口未包含身份认证机制，远程攻击者无需任何凭证即可通过 HSMP 协议直接访问并修改设备配置，实现完全控制。该漏洞影响 Hybrid Networks 线缆调制解调器及配套宽带接入系统的所有版本，攻击者仅需网络可达即可触发，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。目前已有公开的远程配置利用代码。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0791"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-10-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.927","remediation":"升级 Hybrid Networks Cable Broadband Access System 到最新固件版本。在无法升级的情况下，在网络边界防火墙处阻止 HSMP 协议端口（TCP 1812/1813），限制管理接口仅允许受信任的内部 IP 访问。如设备已停止技术支持，建议更换为仍受支持的新款线缆调制解调器设备。禁用远程管理功能可有效降低被远程利用的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/695","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19538","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0791.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0791","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0791.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0791.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e5dfe0fd5272fb57836fe5d2345c8106633847cd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qj7p-33j4-5mh8/GHSA-qj7p-33j4-5mh8.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0791.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2ad23aec-041b-4c90-b661-5c6e9ccd3de1.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0777.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1066","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1066.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1349","title":"Xlink Technology Omni-NFS/X Enterprise 6.1 NFS 守护进程 nfsd.exe 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Xlink Technology Omni-NFS/X Enterprise 6.1 中的 NFS 守护进程 nfsd.exe 存在资源耗尽型拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 111 端口发送设置了 URG（紧急）标志的特定 TCP 数据包，导致 nfsd.exe 消耗大量系统资源，最终使 NFS 服务不可用。该漏洞影响 Omni-NFS/X Enterprise 6.1 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。攻击者无需认证即可触发，但需网络可达目标主机。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1349"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:15.080","remediation":"该产品（Xlink Technology Omni-NFS/X Enterprise 6.1）已停止维护，厂商不再提供安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的 NFS 服务器方案（如 Windows Server 原生 NFS 服务或第三方活跃维护的 NFS 软件）。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上限制对 TCP/UDP 111 端口的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接，并禁用 NFS 服务的 URG 标志包处理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93923679004325&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cveli